data.description:
This duplex in Dutchtown will make a great addition to anyone's rental portfolio. Lower unit is a 1 bed, 1 bath with nice floorplan. The upper unit is a 1 bath studio. Tenants are currently month-to-month until December 31st 2023.
Property is being sold AS-IS and seller makes no warranties of condition.
